==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unwilling
<hw>Un*will"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not willing;
loath; disinclined; reluctant; <as>as, an <ex>unwilling</ex>
servant</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And drop at last, but in <qex>unwilling</qex> ears,⟦br⟧
This saving counsel, ⟦ldquo⟧Keep your piece nine years.⟦rdquo⟧</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un*will"ing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Un*will"ing*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unwind</ent>⟦br⟧
